<section id="changes_4_1_1">
<title>Changes in KaarPux version 4.1.1</title>

<!-- ============================================================ -->

<para>
	&kx; version <systemitem>4.1.1</systemitem> released on <systemitem>2014-feb-07</systemitem>
</para>

<para>
	<itemizedlist>

		<listitem><para>
		Linux Kernel updated to version 3.13.1
		</para></listitem>

		<listitem><para>
		firefox updated to version 27.0
		</para></listitem>

		<listitem><para>
		thunderbird updated to version 24.3.0
		</para></listitem>

		<listitem><para>
		flash_player_11 updated to version 11.2.202.336
		</para></listitem>

		<listitem><para>
		icedtea-web updated to version 1.4.2
		</para></listitem>

		<listitem><para>
		added SANE (Scanner Access Now Easy)
		</para></listitem>

		<listitem><para>
		CUPS (printing) fixed and enabled by default
		</para></listitem>

		<listitem><para>
		added conntrack-tools (User space connection tracking tools for iptables)
		</para></listitem>

		<listitem><para>
		added lxc (Linux Containers)
		</para></listitem>

		<listitem><para>
		bugs fixed, minor improvements and additions
		</para></listitem>

	</itemizedlist>
</para>

